{"tid":1174592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落馬洲95歳老翁以運動褲上吊　兒子發現已太遲","createTime":"2019-05-28T03:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T04:54:15.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5a792e98166e3083ef654ff759845257b608df98","tid":1174592,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"一名姓黃(95歲)老翁，今晨(28日)6時許，被兒子發現在落馬洲上竹園村住所的睡房，以運動褲上吊。消防員接報趕至，隨即將老翁解下，經救護員檢驗後證實不治。警員在場調查，現場沒有檢獲遺書，經初步調查後，相信事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=10c5d60b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528084650332-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190528084650332-0528_00822_001.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=212e2915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528084650332-0528_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9dba8a1fe8b577233e8a94b9b2cf3d8f93b1e0eb","tid":1174592,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e36573f79468fa8f6b2bb4b477483dca9519fb","tid":1174592,"uid":220701,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"2019年<br />\n安樂死呢?"},{"pid":"0922e2